<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>決済完了 - gibtee</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Hiragino Sans', 'Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN', sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      color: #333;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 90%;
      width: 500px;
      background: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .success-icon {
      color: #27AE60;
      font-size: 60px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #27AE60;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .order-number {
      font-weight: bold;
      background: #f1f1f1;
      padding: 8px 15px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .close-button {
      background-color: #27AE60;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    .close-button:hover {
      background-color: #219653;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="success-icon">✅</div>
    <h1>決済が完了しました</h1>
    <p>ご注文ありがとうございます！決済処理が正常に完了しました。</p>
    <div class="order-number">注文番号：<%= orderNumber %></div>
    <p>LINEアプリに戻り、注文ステータスをご確認ください。</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
